  <description type="morphology">Stems to 50 cm × 0.1--0.7 mm. Leaves 6--10.5 cm; blade 0.3--0.5 mm, apex ± obtuse. Inflorescences: peduncles with 0--3[--4] coils, 0.5--16.5 × 0.5 mm. Flowers: pistils 4--8. Fruits 1.8--2 × 0.7--1.5 mm; gynophore 1.2--1.9 cm; beak terminal, slightly recurved, 0.6--1 mm. 2n = 16.</description>
